This directory is for project-local Eleventy shortcodes.

Any `.js` file placed here, or in a subdirectory here, is auto-loaded by
`src/_includes/11ty-starter-common/.eleventy.js` and can register shortcodes
with `eleventyConfig`.

Example:
`src/_includes/shortcodes/card.js`
`src/_includes/shortcodes/sections/sectionHeader.js`
